# Create page embed

See `_docs/PLAN_create_mutate_embed.md` for invariants.

## Rules

- Embed mode: parent owns history; iframe must not `location.reload`, `location.href =`, `assign`, or `replace` for same-origin app routes except via runtime fallbacks for standalone.
- Navigation and post-submit refresh go through `createPageRuntime.js`.
- Submit in embed: `navigate: 'none'` on `submitCreationWithPending`, then `refreshAfterSubmit({ creationId })`.
- Blog editor: `shellOut('/create/blog/:id')` from embed.
- Navigation: `navigate(href)` (in-overlay), `shellOut(href)` (leave overlay), `requestCloseOverlay()` (Escape).
- Basic ↔ advanced: `switchCreateEditorMode('basic'|'advanced')` sets `create_editor` cookie and reloads overlay iframe (`forceReload`); do not shell out to `/create` for mode switches.

Run `npm run check:workflow-embed` after edits to embed-capable files.
